article.description: — Jordan Burns had 26 points as Colgate defeated Boston University 86-79 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Burns scores 26 to lift Colgate over Boston U. 86-79
article.linkText: Burns scores 26 to lift Colgate over Boston U. 86-79
article.story: BOSTON -- — Jordan Burns had 26 points as Colgate defeated Boston University 86-79 on Saturday night. Tucker Richardson had 14 points for Colgate (2-1, 2-1 Patriot League). Nelly Cummings added 14 points. Jack Ferguson had 12 points. Javante McCoy had 16 points for the Terriers (1-2, 1-2). Walter Whyte added 15 points and 11 rebounds. Sukhmail Mathon had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
